Tough boy don''t whine
Tough boy don''t snitch
Tough boy get a tough whooping from his tough daddy
Gotta make sure tough boy don''t flinch
My first memory was family violence, why I''m a bit nihilistic, your highness
I just sit back in the climate, shaded in silence
Shouldn''t complain so I kept it in private
Shots go running through the Southside, poppin''
